com.google.inject.tools.ideplugin
Class GuicePlugin

java.lang.Object
  com.google.inject.tools.ideplugin.GuicePlugin

public abstract class GuicePlugin
extends java.lang.Object

The main object of the plugin. Unfortunately, it must be created in IDE specific ways. Responsible for creating the Injector and building the various objects the plugin needs. This object can be thought of as a wrapper for the Injector.

Author:
Darren Creutz (dcreutz@gmail.com)
